Loadsa modules
==============

  - Connect:      req/res/next
  - Express:      A default happy place
  - Passport:     auth support for nearly all the things
  - Jade:         My preferred view engine this week
  - Stylus:       The CSS sugar that works best on node at the moment
  - Zombie:       Headless browser for the testing
  - Mocha:        My preferred test runner this year
  - Mocha-Cakes:  Sugar, I know
  - Coffeescript: I'm not going to argue about it
  - Should:       I like writing 'should' sometimes 
  - Nodemon:      Keeping the feedback cycle fast forevs
  - Jake:         A formalised build process
